name: Flower Power
description:
Flower Power! Press 'p' for power and 'o' for flower, naturally. Also ->
- Press 'x' to save image as png
- Press 'm' for super duper crazy trooper flower power mode V4.20
Roving camera controls ->
Mouse ->
click : toggle pointer lock
left/right : yaw
up/down : pitch

Keys ->
w/s : forward/backward
e/q : up/down
←/→ : left/right
↑/↓ : forward/backward
+/- : field of view
(pointer lock only)
a/d : yaw | left/right
r/f : pitch | elevation
